Title: Zeroing Debt
Description:
I do hope that is the last we see of the Baron. Truth be told, I respect his seat of power in Stranglethorn.

We were lucky to find Zeros still alive. He must have developed quite the positive relationship with the Baron before all this nonsense, or else he would not have been given so much time.

Let us return to the Archives.

Objectives.Text: Use the portal to return to the Azure Archives
